(5, 'Camp Booties', '<p>\r\n    <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The Forty Below® Camp Booties™ are a great choice as your synthetic insulated camp bootie.&nbsp;WINNER of Best Camp Booties from&nbsp;</span></span><a style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(30, 135, 240);cursor:pointer;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.backpacker.com/gear-item/40-below-camp-booties/\">BACKPACKER Magazine</a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">!</span></span><br>\r\n    <br>\r\n    <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">They provide support and control while walking around camp and help keep your feet warm even if damp. The closed cell foam footbed adds cushion and added insulation, and is removable, so they can be used like a sock when inside a sleeping bag.</span></span><br>\r\n    &nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;padding-left:30px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Lacing:</strong> Goes on the top of the foot and around the ankle, providing support and control when walking around. No more floppy camp booties! The ribbon lace is smooth and comfortable.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Sole material:</strong> A thin rubber fabric (1-2 mm thick) bonded to a slightly stretchy nylon fabric with a small dot pattern, that stays flexible even at -40F and sheds snow easily.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Body fabric:</strong> Taffeta nylon outer fabric upper, which is not coated to allow for maximum moisture to escape from the inside to help them dry fast.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Lower side rand:</strong> Made of Cordura nylon that is waterproof coated and adds durability\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Inner Lining:</strong> made of nylon lining to make them easy to slide socks in and out of them.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Insulation:</strong> Polyester filament insulation goes completely around and under the foot. Made of Lamilite®, a unique and proprietary insulation from Wiggy’s Inc. made from silicone treated continuous filament fiberfill that provides insulation even if wet, as compared to down/feather insulation which provide no insulation when wet. We use Lamilite® brand insulation because it has many unique advantages: The filaments are bonded to the nylon face fabric to allow for maximum thickness and durability. The fibers are treated with silicone, instead of glues/binding agents, so it enables the fibers to spread apart rather than clump together, and allows for water to travel on it for faster drying.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Footbed:</strong> The removable 1/4″ thick closed cell foam adds cushion and insulation. This is unique, enabling you to take them out for the technique to wear them inside a double shelled mountaineering or ski boot when its regular liner is removed for drying, enabling you to wear your boots in camp with cozy camp booties inside. The feature also enables them to be worn like a sock, making it also functional to wear these inside a sleeping bag and allow for the foot to move more freely in the bottom.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Machine or hand washable:</strong> Remove lacing first, use mild soap or detergent, and Air Dry or Low Heat setting on dryer.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Hand Crafted in the USA!</span></span><br>\r\n    &nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;padding-left:30px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            Small: <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">US&nbsp;W</strong> 5-7 (fits a foot length up to 9.0 inches/23cm).\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            Medium: <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">US</strong> <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">M</strong> 7-9.5, <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">W</strong> 7.5-10&nbsp;(fits a foot length up to 10 inches/25.5cm)\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            Large: <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">US</strong> <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">M</strong> 10-12, <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">W</strong> 10.5+&nbsp;(fits a foot length up to 11 inches/28cm)\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            Extra Large:&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">US M</strong> 12.5-15 (fits a foot length up to 12 inches/34.5cm)\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:bolder;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Weight:</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">&nbsp;10oz / 295g (per pair-size Medium)</span></span>\r\n</p>', 4, 'Booties', 'https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/spai/q_lossy+ret_img+to_auto/https://www.alpineascents.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/43d903ca-e4f4-49cb-987a-8a5b68c22389.jpeg', 'Forty Below Ltd.', NULL, '79.95', 100, 0),
(6, 'Coolmax® Hiker Micro Crew Midweight Sock Men’s', '<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;margin:0px 0px 20px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    The perfect sock for climbers looking to lose bulk without sacrificing cushioning and comfort when the weather gets a little warmer.<br>\r\n    <br>\r\n    Cushioning is provided by soft terry loops underfoot and targeted protection over the ankle and achilles provides a perfect amount of support and comfort. While a smooth, performance fit assures there’s no slipping, no bunching, and no blisters.&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;padding-left:30px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-in