oto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><code><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"> is perfect for high altitude peaks and now tells a more sustainable story.&nbsp; Scarpa have used more environmentally-friendly materials in its construction, while still offering the same great performance&nbsp;that their boots are renowned for.</span></code></span><br>\r\n    <br>\r\n    <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><code><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">With a fully waterproof shell and mid-calf gaiter, this boot can keep out even the heaviest of storms. The PrimaLoft synthetic insulation lining on the inner boot wraps your feet in a warm shell, no matter how fast the temps drop. And with a lightweight Vibram Precision Tech Roll sole with a shock-absorbing midsole, you’ll feel fresh no matter how many steps it takes to get to the top.</span></code></span><br>\r\n    &nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;padding-left:30px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Gaiter:</strong>&nbsp;KCN-Tech Schoeller water repellent fabric + elastic S-Tech Schoeller fabric + Super-Fabric, laminated with an Hdry® membrane to guarantee maximum waterproof performance. Light PU rand for protection and containment of the heel.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Inner shell</strong>&nbsp;High-tenacity water-repellent microfiber + EVA + 3mm Cork to ensure maximum insulation.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Lacing system:</strong>&nbsp;Outer closure: Flex Seal, waterproof zip.&nbsp;Internal closure: Fast lock system, a quick closing system with Dyneema® cord and intermediate pull-tab, to progressively wrap the foot.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Removable liner</strong>: high density EVA 2mm + Primaloft micro-fleece with Velcro closure to make it easier to put on and to ensure maximum insulation.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Insole:</strong>&nbsp;Carbon with differentiated thicknesses for great torsion control and lightness; upper EVA coating for maximum comfort and insulation. Removable insole: 37.5® fabric (upper section) + Aluminum (mid section), dual density EVA lower section for maximum insulation.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <code><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Sole:</strong>&nbsp;Vibram® 0 Gravity V-Lite. Compatible with automatic crampons.</code>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    <code><strong style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:bolder;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Sizing:&nbsp;</strong></code><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-ap