(47, 'Lightyear Goggles', '<div class=\"overview\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    <p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px 0px 20px;\">\r\n        The award-winning Lightyear goggles combine the revolutionary <a style=\"background-color:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(255, 82, 0) !important;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://julbo.us/collections/superflowpro\">SuperFlow Pro</a> anti-fog magnetic ventilation system with a frameless design and an XL-sized REACTIV photochromic lens. The new SuperFlow Pro easily switches open to immediately eliminate fog and prevent moisture buildup, replacing the Aerospace goggle’s hinge system with a glove-friendly design and dual-sided magnetic closure that effortlessly locks the lens to the frame. Combined with Julbo’s REACTIV photochromic technology, this large, spherical-lensed goggle is a multi-tasking hero for all conditions.<br>\r\n        <br>\r\n        The <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Spectron 3&nbsp;polycarbonate lens</strong> are shatterproof and combine superior optical quality and proprietary anti-fog double lens technology (guaranteeing clear and protected vision), while providing&nbsp;category 3 protection from the suns UV ray\'s (VLT 13%).<br>\r\n        <br>\r\n        Other key features:\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:20px;orphans:2;padding-left:30px;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Air Flow: </strong>Ventilation incorporated into the frame and lens promotes air circulation to prevent fogging.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Anti Fog Coating: </strong>The inner surface of the lens has an additional coating to prevent fog buildup.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Wide, Double-Adjustable Strap: </strong>The 45mm-wide strap has assertive style and guaranteed grip. Two loops on either side allow for symmetrical adjustability and compatibility with all helmet types and sizes.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Dual-Density Foam: </strong>Two layers of foam provide an optimal fit, with a soft-touch layer for comfort against the skin.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Frameless Construction: </strong>The minimalist frame gives an extra-wide field of view with zero obstruction laterally and vertically. The strap is inserted directly into the frame for a minimalist look.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Full Silicone Strap: </strong>Three silicone strips ensure perfect grip.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"technical-description\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\r\n        <p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\r\n            <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Ventilated Lens:&nbsp;</strong>Additional ventilation via the lens prevents any fogging<strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">.</strong>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n    <span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Further considerations when making your google choice can be found&nbsp;</span></span><a style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(30, 135, 240);cursor:pointer;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.alpineascents.com/blog/gear/goggles-for-the-mountains/\">HERE</a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(33,37,41);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.98px;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">.</span></span>\r\n</p>', 5, 'Eyewear', 'https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/spai/q_lossy+ret_img+to_auto/https://www.alpineascents.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/02bab228-613a-447f-a687-29e010e28272-1-600x300.jpeg', 'Julbo', NULL, '199.95', 100, NULL);
